    <!-- First-run disclaimer -->
    <string name="disclaimer_title">Before you start</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_body">ClimaPilot is an independent app and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or supported by Midea. It controls compatible air conditioners over your local Wi-Fi.\n\nMake sure your unit is correctly installed and safe to operate before sending commands. You use this app at your own risk; the authors accept no liability for any damage or loss.\n\nMeasured values such as power are provided by the device and may be inaccurate.\n\nNote: the first time you connect to a device, ClimaPilot fetches a one-time access token from Midea\'s server (no account needed). After that, control runs fully locally — you can even deny the app internet access.</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_accept">I understand</string>

